name: Phenakistoscope - 1893
description:
This is a version of Eadweard Muybridge's Phenakistoscope: A Couple Waltzing, which has been exactly straightened to the alignment markers on the original image, the extra elements of the image removed, and the edges cleaned up against a plain white background. This is to allow experience of the art without the technical distraction of the copyright notice, dust, and adjacent repeated animations.
Date	1893
